  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: Other shapes' blood, sweat, and tears went into it.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
    eventReference:
      eventRef:
        Guid:
          Data1: 0
          Data2: 0
          Data3: 0
          Data4: 0
        Path: 
  - dialogueSpeakerDatum: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 898383444ddfe8447aa8ed4370564c42, type: 2}
    text: And they are making me a lot of money.
    hasVoiceActing: 0
